T1  - Rational Expectations Model of Term Premia with Some Implications for Empirical Asset Demand Equations
AU  - WALSH, CARL E.
Y1  - 1985/03/01
PY  - 1985
DA  - 1985/03/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6261.1985.tb04937.x
